node.text: Please try and take time today to appreciate how great your life is because of the people that sacrificed their lives on this day 20 years ago. We will never forgive. We will never forget. The pain that was caused still takes over my body every year on this day. For those families still feeling the pain of their loved ones who lost their lives this day, our hearts go out to you. Nothing will ever take that pain away and no amount of sympathy or apology will cut it. To my fellow Americans, we love you. We must stick together through every adversity.
